{"tid":1821391,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"外國巴打展覽緊，點解無人捐？（歐洲巡迴展眾籌）","createTime":"2020-01-12T08:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T08:32:00.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"773b95788a7b5bf3207cfdf7a55ee3192d0c9a7c","tid":1821391,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:59:23.000Z","msg":"眾籌網址 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Ffree-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=6a731694\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/free-hong-kong-europe-touring-exhibition</a><br />\n<br />\n各位手足，我哋係Free Hong Kong Exhibition團隊，由一班海外香港人組成，主要打國際戰線。我哋希望以巡迴展覧嘅形式，將香港人嘅聲音帶到海外。作為响城牆外面生活嘅人，我哋自覺有責任將港共政府嘅所作所為話俾全世界知。响西方民主社會，人民就係力量，政府嘅決策同立法往往都以民意為依歸，而展覽正正可以提供一個空間同平台，直接同市民接觸交流。我哋希望以普羅大眾為出發點，提高民間對香港事態嘅關注，團結國際民運陣線，希望响國際間有更加多迴響，間接向港共政府施壓。<br />\n<br />\n好耐都未夠數<br />\n外國巴打努力緊 <br />\n岩岩仲比中共打壓烏克蘭展覽<br />\n麻煩大家幫手捐一捐"},{"pid":"913825099a249891289e0139210bab7c28d0a3f4","tid":1821391,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T09:02:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b7d6d696d95ed9e237c08b2a223c351dad3a502","tid":1821391,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T14:29:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9d6187d0e0673a82c860d0cffb98454d9a64d6","tid":1821391,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T14:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862c460487968c6b4fbb2b3cd5df4f41b6dc3d5b","tid":1821391,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T19:50:24.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3ac3a0a3680036c222b4e6b612b51c289eef1b","tid":1821391,